get repository:
git clone https://github.com/AVR-GCC/ArduinoAnalyzer.git <target directory>

to see which files you changed:
git status

to add a file to next commit:
git add <target file>

to commit:
git commit -m "update message"

after commit, merge:
git pull --rebase

then save changes:
git push

update current repository:
git pull

for single file:
git checkout <file path>

